===Analysis===
'''Arare Kai'''

Priority: '''Low'''

:At first remodel, she has low firepower and a decent torpedo stat, making her hitting harder in night battle than at day, but not great at either.
:While not impressive in combat, do keep in mind than many maps require you to bring at least a few destroyers for routing.
:Furthermore, destroyers are cheap to deploy and can equip [[Drum Canister]], making them suited for expeditions.


'''Arare Kai Ni'''  

Priority: '''Medium-High'''
:Her second remodel increases her Firepower, Torpedo and ASW stat to very high levels for a destroyers, making her very well suited for both surface combat and anti-submarine warfare.
:Furthermore, she gains the ability to load [[Daihatsu]] and tanks, allowing her to increase expedition income or be deployed against enemy installations.
:Keep in mind that this remodel requires a [[Blueprint]].


====Recommended Roles====
* Surface combat (Second remodel)
* Anti-installation (Second remodel)
* ASW (Second remodel)
* Expeditions (Second remodel)

===Important Information===
* Required for A32, A87, B21 and B116
* An option for C25

